      "prompt": "Search the internet for new manufacturing, pharmaceutical, nutraceutical, and industrial companies. Identify decision makers such as VP Operations, Manufacturing Directors, Engineering Leaders, or R&D heads. Summarize company name, industry, leadership contact, and why they may need tooling, automation, or manufacturing optimization. Output a structured research report.",
